               <msContents>
                  <summary>I Taʾāmmǝra Māryām: I-1) Maṣḥafa śǝrʿāt, The rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols. 3ra-8ra)&#xD; I-2)
                     ʾƎsaggǝd laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki... “I worship Thee…” (fols. 8ra-9rb)&#xD; I-3)

                     Introductory exhortation (fols. 9rb-11va)&#xD; I-4) Taʾammǝra Māryām “Miracles of
                     Mary”: ca. 25 miracles (fols. 11va-32va)&#xD; II) Miracles of the Trinity,
                     Archangel Michael, Jesus (fols. 32va-37rb)&#xD; I-5) A hymn to the Virgin
                     (fols. 38ra-39ra)&#xD; III) Taʾammǝra Gabra Manfas Qǝddus "Miracles of Gabra Manfas Qǝddus": 2 miracles (fols. 38ra-41rb).</summary>
                 
